snippet.title: ☆ INTRO TO BOX AND WHISKER PLOTS!
snippet.description:
Join us on this flipped math lesson where we visually explore how to construct and analyze a box-and-whisker plot. For more MashUp Math content, visit http://www.mashupmath.com and join our free mailing list! :)

This lesson answers the questions: What is a box and whisker plot? How do I make a box and whisker plot? What is an interquartile range? How do I find the upper quartile? How do I find the lower quartile?

Our lessons are perfect for flipped classroom math teachers and students. This lesson is aligned with the common core learning standards for math and the SAT math curriculum as well.

Be sure to join our mailing list at http://www.mashupmath.com
